# Testing And Proof

No work packet is complete without proof.

Acceptable proof includes:

- tests passing
- service boot output
- curl command output
- migration applied successfully
- Docker Compose service healthy
- UI route visible
- Playwright/browser verification
- logs showing full demo step
- screenshot path or trace ID

Every agent report must include:

- files changed
- commands run
- proof produced
- blockers
- next step

For integration work, proof must show cross-service behavior, not only isolated unit success.
